entry.title: China, U.S. Trade Climate Barbs as Ties Fray
entry.content: Once a rare bright spot, the fight against global warming is the latest source of tension between the world’s top greenhouse-gas emitters.

entry.title: Ukraine Strikes Russian Base Ahead of Talks With Turkey, U.N.
entry.content: Ukraine’s latest attack in Russian-occupied Kherson came as President Volodymyr Zelensky prepared to meet with foreign leaders and discuss food shipments and the increasingly tense situation at the Zaporizhzhia nuclear plant.
